{"tid":1507613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日到底有咩活動搞到封西環？","createTime":"2019-08-26T08:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:50:57.000Z","uid":161374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95cdad81922928d17d5fb4b7b7a13f8d03f09c31","tid":1507613,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/26/P2019082600429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F26%2FP2019082600429.htm&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=4c198d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/26/P2019082600429.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港島特別交通安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　警方將於明日（八月二十七日）實施特別交通安排，配合於港島舉行的一項公眾活動。<br />\n<br />\n　　下列道路將於上午九時三十分起實施間歇性封閉，直至人群散去及交通回復正常為止：<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;　皇后大道西；<br />\n&mdash;　屈地街；<br />\n&mdash;　朝光街；<br />\n&mdash;　德輔道西；<br />\n&mdash;　堅彌地城海旁；<br />\n&mdash;　山道；及<br />\n&mdash;　保德街。<br />\n<br />\n　　道路封閉期間，車輛將可能被禁止進出沿途的停車場。<br />\n<br />\n　　警方會視乎該區當時的交通及人潮情況實施交通安排。駕車人士應保持忍讓，並遵從現場警務人員的指示。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月26日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間12時00分"},{"pid":"ee66265f1870b703433a85baf97be4c35030fd9f","tid":1507613,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=00dcc34b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"920d09e5e707c30267f0516281dfbc4d3fbad82a","tid":1507613,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee66265f1870b703433a85baf97be4c35030fd9f",